title: Dyno Run: Lexus IS350 (2006-09) with a Takeda Cold Air Intake
description: This Lexus IS350 nets +13 hp and +11 ft/lbs of torque on the dyno with a Cold Air Intake from Takeda (AFE).
tags: Takeda Cold Air Intake, CAI, Cold Air Intakes

asset.title: Dyno: Lexus IS350 (2006-09) with a Takeda Cold Air Intake (CAI)
asset.description:
A Lexus IS350 on the dyno with a Cold Air Intake from  Takeda (AFE). The IS350's only modification is the CAI and it nets +13 horsepower and +11 ft-lbs of torque. 

Find out how much power your vehicle can gain with a Takeda Intake by heading over to AutoAnything: http://www.autoanything.com/air-intakes/73A5155A0A0.aspx

View all air intake products here: http://www.autoanything.com/air-intakes/10A50208.aspx
